Package com.gliffy.restunit

Core classes for RESTUnit.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BodyCall A call of a request that has a body.
BodyResponse A response that has a body.
Executor Handles the nuts and bolts of executing one call.
GetCall An call to a GET endpoint.
RestCall A call to a REST endpoint.
RestCallResponse An expected response.
RestCallResult The results of a RestCall having been executed.
RestTest A test for a REST endpoint.
RestTestResult Results of running a RestTest.
RestUnit Entry point to RESTUnit test execution.
ResultFormatter Formats results for some readability.
TestNGRestUnit Allows using RESTUnit inside TestNG.
 

Enum Summary
Result The results of running a test.
SSLRequirement Indicates requirements for a test regarding SSL support.
